text:
straykids:
bangchan: you are the best leader. you are perfect the way you are. you are the leader anyone would ask for and you chose the perfect members for your group… remember that all the stays love you and so do your members. we love you for you and the way you are. you’re doing a great job, and you always have been. we love you!♥️

leeknow: you might not be able to understand this, but i hope you can. us stays love you for all you do. like when it comes to your smooth dance moves, or your leadership. i hope you know that stays and your members love you dearly. we love you, leeknow!♥️

changbin: you are worth it. you’re perfect for you. we get that you love to work out but others don’t. don’t listen to them, listen to us, and your members. we love you for you and your passion to work out. your rapping is really nice too! stays and your members love you. i hope you keep doing what you love and ignore anyone who tells you otherwise! we love you!♥️

hyunjin: okay, we get it. your extremely handsome, it should be illegal to be that handsome! stays love you for you! not just because of your look, but because of your personality! you’re bright, yet like a prince. i hope you know how much stays and your members love you. we love you!♥️

han: okay, there’s our ace of kpop! your vocals and raps are beautiful! even non-stays would agree! and the way you dance is on point! i’m glad you’re having a good time! us stays and your members love you!♥️

felix: here’s our sunshine! we love how bright and happy you are! it’s like you’re the sun of the group! and we love you for that. i’m happy you know how happy we are for you! i hope you know how much your members love you! we love you too!♥️

seungmin: we understand, you’re pretty savage. don’t get me wrong, we love you for that. we love how you have feisty comebacks, but you never mean it. your members love you dearly, and i hope you know that! we love you too!♥️

jeongin: the makne. we love you, our baby bread! you may be getting older, but we will still call you baby bread! you are so cute yet so handsome! i guess that’s why you’re the ‘makne on top’! i hope you spend the rest of your time in the group being a happy makne! we love you!♥️

we’re so proud of you guys!♥️ 
#skz #straykids #bangchan #leeknow #changbin #hyunjin #han #felix #seungmin #jeongin
